aria-label='' role="img"> </div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__7428234401716749704459' data-elem-id='1716749704459' data-elem-type='shape' data-field-top-value="360" data-field-left-value="80" data-field-height-value="170" data-field-width-value="510" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px"> <div class='tn-atom'> </div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__7428234401716749716540' data-elem-id='1716749716540' data-elem-type='shape' data-field-top-value="360" data-field-left-value="610" data-field-height-value="175" data-field-width-value="510" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px"> <div class='tn-atom'> </div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__7428234401716749860818' data-elem-id='1716749860818' data-elem-type='text' data-field-top-value="392" data-field-left-value="112" data-field-height-value="105" data-field-width-value="411" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-field-textfit-value="autoheight" data-field-fontsize-value="14" data-field-left-res-960-value="60px"> <div class='tn-atom'field='tn_text_1716749860818'>CommuniGate Pro 6.3 предоставляется бесплатно <br>для ознакомления и&nbsp;тестирования до&nbsp;семи пользователей, без ограничений по&nbsp;времени. Для приобретения лицензий на&nbsp;большее количество пользователей, пожалуйста, обращайтесь в&nbsp;наш отдел продаж <a href="mailto:sales@communigatepro.ru" style="font-weight: 500; color: rgb(52, 55, 250); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(52, 55, 250); box-shadow: none; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">sales@communigatepro.ru</a></div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__7428234401716750065433' data-elem-id='1716750065433' data-elem-type='text' data-field-top-value="392" data-field-left-value="642" data-field-height-value="84" data-field-width-value="409" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-field-textfit-value="autoheight" data-field-fontsize-value="14" data-field-left-res-960-value="70px"> <div class='tn-atom'field='tn_text_1716750065433'>По&nbsp;всем вопросам, связанным с&nbsp;использованием и&nbsp;лицензированием CommuniGate Pro, дополнительных модулей, плагинов и&nbsp;клиентских приложений, вы&nbsp;можете обращаться <a href="mailto:support@communigatepro.ru" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="color: rgb(52, 55, 250); font-weight: 500;"> </a><a href="mailto:support@communigatepro.ru" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" style="color: rgb(52, 55, 250); font-weight: 500; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(52, 55, 250); box-shadow: none; text-decoration: none;"> support@communigatepro.ru</a></div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__7428234401715775494466' data-elem-id='1715775494466' data-elem-type='shape' data-field-top-value="268" data-field-left-value="112" data-field-height-value="40" data-field-width-value="40" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px"> <div class='tn-atom'> </div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__7428234401715774403374 t396__elem--anim-hidden' data-elem-id='1715774403374' data-elem-type='shape' data-field-top-value="139" data-field-left-value="111" data-field-height-value="169" data-field-width-value="483" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-animate-sbs-event="hover" data-animate-sbs-trgels="1715775494466" data-animate-sbs-opts="[{'mx':0,'my':0,'sx':1,'sy':1,'op':1,'ro':0,'ti':0,'ea':'0','dt':0},{'mx':0,'my':0,'sx':1,'sy':1,'op':0,'ro':0,'ti':0,'ea':'0','dt':0},{'mx':0,'my':0,'sx':1,'sy':1,'op':1,'ro':0,'ti':300,'ea':'easeInOut','dt':0}]" data-field-top-res-960-value="60px" data-field-left-res-960-value="30px" data-field-width-res-960-value="940"> <div class='tn-atom'> </div> </div> <div class='t396__elem tn-elem tn-elem__7428234401715774463073 t396__elem--anim-hidden' data-elem-id='1715774463073' data-elem-type='text' data-field-top-value="171" data-field-left-value="143" data-field-height-value="105" data-field-width-value="419" data-field-axisy-value="top" data-field-axisx-value="left" data-field-container-value="grid" data-field-topunits-value="px" data-field-leftunits-value="px" data-field-heightunits-value="px" data-field-widthunits-value="px" data-animate-sbs-event="hover" data-animate-sbs-trgels="1715775494466" data-animate-sbs-opts="[{'mx':0,'my':0,'sx':1,'sy':1,'op':1,'ro':0,'ti':0,'ea':'0','dt':0},{'mx':0,'my':0,'sx':1,'sy':1,'op':0,'ro':0,'ti':0,'ea':'0','dt':0},{'mx':0,'my':0,'sx':1,'sy':1,'op':1,'ro':0,'ti':300,'ea':'easeInOut','dt':0}]" data-field-textfit-value="autoheight" data-field-fontsize-value="14" data-field-left-res-960-value="60px"> <div class='tn-atom'field='tn_text_1715774463073'>Для коммерческого использования актуальных версий <span style="font-weight: 600;">CommuniGate Pro </span><span style="font-weight: 600; color: rgb(52, 55, 250);">6.3</span> свыше семи пользователей, должна быть действующая техническая поддержка, приобретенная у&nbsp;авторизованных партнеров